"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T04:26:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>華人最叻係咩 就係內鬥權鬥<br />\n加上白鴿班老野一早都唔妥許依個新生派<br />\n依家機會來了 仲唔做過順水人情俾建制<br />\n班老野為他日入政府決策部做足準備</blockquote><strong>黎智英曾拍片盲撐保證許智峯「有幹勁有操守」</strong><br />\n<br />\n由《蘋果動新聞》在2016年9月4日上載，即立法會換屆選舉投票當日，片中黎智英和許智峯並排而坐，黎先多次強調市民要「眼光雪亮」，其後就「力銷」當時嘅港島區候選人許智峯，稱「我對呢個人(許智峯)嘅幹勁，對呢個人嘅操守，對呢個人做事嗰種堅強，我係可以保證、可以承擔」，黎在片中又指許是「一片丹心」，稱「呢啲後生仔入咗去(立法會)會為我哋香港做事」。至於許智峯亦在片中稱，「從政嘅人要有良知」。<br />\n<br />\n&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/lihkg/dog1.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt;</blockquote>笑撚死</blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/26/211502_efb89a8419473f80410a54fc07a8425a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F211502_efb89a8419473f80410a54fc07a8425a.jpg&h=be2fca64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U1n2tHe3KVA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DU1n2tHe3KVA&d=Cafjcg0goWczJSZ7u65liRFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=a03364d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U1n2tHe3KVA</a></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">就算信你冇存心非禮，你呢隻僭共大愛支IQ，EQ，AQ，乜Q都咁賤值幾十萬一個月？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你Career已經變『石油玩家』：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n玩<br />\n<br />\n能<br />\n<br />\n源<br />\n<br />\n啦<br />\n<br />\n！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"59dacb56913df69bfb97dc175dbf856fa1929cb6","tid":644587,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit